column1: Regular traffic reports will resume Thursday October 11 at 4:00 p.m.

column4: Inbound Winchester Rd is shutdown at Sir Barton Way due to a serious collision at Patchen Wilkes Dr.
Detour to Sir Barton Way to either Liberty Rd or Man O War Blvd.
Two outbound lanes are open with traffic moving slowly.
NOTE:  Meeting St (off Sir Barton Way) is closed to thru traffic due to no access back to inbound Winchester Rd.
UPDATE 3:23 p.m. - Inbound Winchester Rd at Sir Barton Way is now open.  The right lane remains blocked on Winchester Rd at Patchen Wilkes Dr.
